data.description: This town home is a MUST SEE! Beautiful mature trees in the front common lawn area. New tile in the kitchen! Open Kitchen and Dining area that leads out to your private patio and hot tub. Half bath on the main floor. Tinted windows throughout the home. Big Master bedroom, Bath has large soaker tub. Close to shopping! Come and see your new town home today!
